== Typical Brainless Speak ==
*Perspective is why I date girls with small hands.
*There are many things in our society worth throwing a few bucks at, most of them dance the pole.
*You might try wiping the elitest masturabatory stink off your fingers, especially if you're gonna have Tacos.

== Random Examples of Trollery ==
*Appearing as [[homosexual|mrsaturdaynight]], brainless admits that he [http://www.livejournal.com/community/debate/3388463.html thinks a terrorist walks a higher moral ground than an abortionist does]
*[[dancingdrew]] gets upset when brainlesswonder argues that all men are potential rapists. He bans him from his journal when he points out that [http://www.livejournal.com/users/dancingdrew/144992.html half his friends agree].
*[[paigegirl]] flies off the handle when brainlesswonder suggests that rape is humorous and therapeutic. She begins [http://www.livejournal.com/community/debate/2930332.html deleting her own comments].
*[http://www.livejournal.com/community/bisexual/609613.html suggesting that bisexuals who stay in the closet are selfish.]
*[[liberal|liberals]] get bent out of shape when brainlesswonder suggests that abortion is a [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2017234.html cosmetic procedure.]
*[http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2134453.html Praising the California legal system] sends [[liberal|liberals]] into a fit of rage. Includes another appearance by [[paigegirl]] who "outs" [[homosexual|r_u_mental]] as brainlesswonder.
*In a thread that starts, yet again, with [[paigegirl]] [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2093087.html?thread=38854943#t38854943 getting pissed], brainless makes appearances as [[homosexual|furries_r_gay]], [[homosexual|burka_humper]], [[homosexual|jesus_slurpee]], [[homosexual|marxist_is_mean]], [[homosexual|not_brainless]], and flim_flam_man.
*Flipping the "Christians are idiots" standard troll over, similar results were gained by suggesting that [http://www.livejournal.com/community/debate/3639778.html Christian Beliefs are no more illogical than liberal beliefs]
*[[iworshipsatin]] is annoyed at being called [http://www.livejournal.com/community/debate/515022.html?thread=12207822#t12207822 a crippled cunt]

